| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-5726 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: cd842c18-8a2e-570f-8020-aeb9ac69ef3d"
